{
  "id": "829983520",
  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"__TZt8lJ\">1</p><p data-pid=\"HDy6ibWL\">前段时间，有个小学给孩子们开设了一门特别的“兴趣课”——女生学打毛衣、男生学“做飞机”“造火箭”“装汽车”。学校表示，这么做是为了纠正现在的“男孩、女孩性别错位的现象。”在这所学校的校长看来，“男孩应该豪气蓬勃，女孩该宁静温婉”，但现在的孩子们都在一条轨道上被塑造，都缺乏这种环境。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-529171f0472f7b190eb856c0da3d05b3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1643\" data-original-token=\"v2-94fb682f46d9edf76a3d47da10e998ab\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-106c6ee99df147c8570459e3ec49d780_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-529171f0472f7b190eb856c0da3d05b3_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='1643'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1643\" data-original-token=\"v2-94fb682f46d9edf76a3d47da10e998ab\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-106c6ee99df147c8570459e3ec49d780_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-529171f0472f7b190eb856c0da3d05b3_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-529171f0472f7b190eb856c0da3d05b3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"mv1-wBmA\">这下网友们不乐意了：这是性别专属课还是性别歧视课？谁说女孩只能织毛衣、男孩只能造飞机了？</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3e6751175d206e265f2e98cfacbd6e99_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"675\" data-rawheight=\"760\" data-original-token=\"v2-fdd4e6aec69258eff794ebefd3d7a73b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9e5039b88c4eee34ff1ebefe75566a3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"675\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3e6751175d206e265f2e98cfacbd6e99_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='675' height='760'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"675\" data-rawheight=\"760\" data-original-token=\"v2-fdd4e6aec69258eff794ebefd3d7a73b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9e5039b88c4eee34ff1ebefe75566a3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"675\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3e6751175d206e265f2e98cfacbd6e99_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3e6751175d206e265f2e98cfacbd6e99_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"nwAqtYbS\">也难怪大家反应这么大：全世界都在努力破除<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=180972947&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%81%8F%E8%A7%81&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别偏见<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，怎么这里反而要开个这样的兴趣班？要知道这样的偏见和观念，无论对男孩还是女孩都没什么好处！</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"ExIje8kY\">2</p><p data-pid=\"ybUOzge0\">BBC有一部纪录片《男女不再有别》，讲的就是<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=180972947&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%88%BB%E6%9D%BF%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别刻板印象<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>对孩子成长的弊端和不良影响。纪录片中，英国医生贾维德与伦敦大学心理学家合作，做了一系列关于<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=180972947&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别角色<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的实验。就拿很多人都会觉得：男孩天生就是喜欢小汽车，女孩就是喜欢毛绒娃娃。但真的是这样吗？贾维德的婴儿组实验里，让男孩换成女孩的衣服，女孩换成男孩的衣服，然后让志愿者一对一带他们玩。结果志愿者在陪穿女孩衣服的男孩玩的时候，在众多玩具中挑选了小娃娃。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-945540d364395ce294dd9ac3d3ba3eac_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-fec02c9a99d268f08ea3e84a37f9f8af\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-77b0c8269542d33c6e392139ed1ce213_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-945540d364395ce294dd9ac3d3ba3eac_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-fec02c9a99d268f08ea3e84a37f9f8af\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-77b0c8269542d33c6e392139ed1ce213_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-945540d364395ce294dd9ac3d3ba3eac_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-945540d364395ce294dd9ac3d3ba3eac_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"5RdNtwYX\">而穿上男孩衣服的女孩，则被志愿者则很自然地抱到玩具车上。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-afd9a666e5a4467b3e9c333c487436ae_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-7bb24b7530c5d1278be67693b2986125\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2830227e3fb7801e3503b756c659a9c1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-afd9a666e5a4467b3e9c333c487436ae_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-7bb24b7530c5d1278be67693b2986125\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2830227e3fb7801e3503b756c659a9c1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-afd9a666e5a4467b3e9c333c487436ae_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-afd9a666e5a4467b3e9c333c487436ae_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a6556c716b2cf82d220b7be4ea5e853_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-d43d636d05198953d3d12ac1a9e674e0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e37813bf9f112440974b90731ba96f0a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2a6556c716b2cf82d220b7be4ea5e853_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-d43d636d05198953d3d12ac1a9e674e0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e37813bf9f112440974b90731ba96f0a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2a6556c716b2cf82d220b7be4ea5e853_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a6556c716b2cf82d220b7be4ea5e853_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"N6DdSG2l\">后面的几位志愿者也都无一例外：不自觉地给穿女孩衣服的孩子玩娃娃，给穿男孩衣服的孩子玩机器人和形状拼图。当贾维德告诉志愿者们真相时，无比震惊的他们才意识到：因为刻板印象，自己不自觉中替孩子做了选择。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5779dd6b111564125a05909c9ec26fd1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-7d92b6b7bf20dd7865c2a84cb1f05735\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-52510c10521fbc844c67926d442dc79f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5779dd6b111564125a05909c9ec26fd1_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-7d92b6b7bf20dd7865c2a84cb1f05735\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-52510c10521fbc844c67926d442dc79f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5779dd6b111564125a05909c9ec26fd1_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5779dd6b111564125a05909c9ec26fd1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c2102c646d3ed77675bbbdb319a3d55_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-39cf687f500591e22dbffcc1dd24170b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-94b1f12ca9ee318cc918aede3080bde3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6c2102c646d3ed77675bbbdb319a3d55_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-39cf687f500591e22dbffcc1dd24170b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-94b1f12ca9ee318cc918aede3080bde3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6c2102c646d3ed77675bbbdb319a3d55_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c2102c646d3ed77675bbbdb319a3d55_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"07BR-1nZ\">认识到这些，志愿者反思到：<b>我们想教育孩子，你可以成为任何你想要成为的样子，但我们还是在把某个身份强加在孩子身上。</b></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4aa69fc6cff62ed997e03a0b4bb84ea1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"725\" data-original-token=\"v2-d35db2f5e61b27ceba21109d6ff53188\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d7750d4da355ee9e633c6c18bb27bd21_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4aa69fc6cff62ed997e03a0b4bb84ea1_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1000' height='725'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"725\" data-original-token=\"v2-d35db2f5e61b27ceba21109d6ff53188\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d7750d4da355ee9e633c6c18bb27bd21_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4aa69fc6cff62ed997e03a0b4bb84ea1_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4aa69fc6cff62ed997e03a0b4bb84ea1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"hwfeRPl3\">这句话，又是我们现实生活中多少父母和老师的写照呢？在日常生活中，我们有没有在无形中给孩子设下了限制：“你是女孩子，女孩要有女孩的样子。”“你是男孩，怎么像个女孩一个哭哭啼啼的，男孩要坚强。”我们的话语体系，家校氛围，无时无刻不在向孩子输送着无数微小的讯息，这些讯息汇聚在一起，无形之中就定义了孩子，同时也限制了孩子。</p><p data-pid=\"jaSVLxXz\">3</p><p data-pid=\"0Q5BH1im\"><b>就连人们习惯性认为的男孩天然理科好、女孩天然文科强，也被证明是偏见塑造的结果——</b></p><p data-pid=\"riCcicS0\">专家们做了这样一个实验：集中玩俄罗斯方块的女孩们，结果发现她们脑内结构中的一部分的确发生了改变，也就是说俄罗斯方块的训练导致了相应的生理变化、让<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=180972947&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">空间认知能力<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>提高了。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0a12bd3de13d969b6488005c3473bd4_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"968\" data-rawheight=\"546\" data-original-token=\"v2-322cee89bbb482e191344dee290861c9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f9753a6050fe243606a6e4c49e2a72a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"968\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f0a12bd3de13d969b6488005c3473bd4_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='968' height='546'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"968\" data-rawheight=\"546\" data-original-token=\"v2-322cee89bbb482e191344dee290861c9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f9753a6050fe243606a6e4c49e2a72a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"968\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f0a12bd3de13d969b6488005c3473bd4_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0a12bd3de13d969b6488005c3473bd4_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"mh3N5VIS\">负责实验的英国神经成像研究的顶尖专家吉娜教授总结到：<b>男孩空间能力之所以比女孩强，很大程度上是因为受到了更多的鼓励，或者说，男孩在视觉和空间技能的锻炼上更有经验。</b></p><p data-pid=\"Nd5rbhoo\">大脑得到过相关锻炼的男孩，也就更容易发展这种能力，而这种能力又会影响数学、科学等学科的能力。</p><p data-pid=\"lijCWUz4\">所以，吉娜教授给出了颠覆性的答案：<b>男女大脑几乎不存在结构差异。</b></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-02acc4db6957320140a9831c2d54c1da_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-509d549a1ccf5c65d1af6fd8191d7d0d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dd4a9340d1430a6e52609928a56a3f6d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-02acc4db6957320140a9831c2d54c1da_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-509d549a1ccf5c65d1af6fd8191d7d0d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dd4a9340d1430a6e52609928a56a3f6d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-02acc4db6957320140a9831c2d54c1da_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-02acc4db6957320140a9831c2d54c1da_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ffc4253f4787ba845f2110a772cbb9d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"1861\" data-original-token=\"v2-ed3c6453525a180d741dce8adf396c97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8385dc18e935335feabe320006ae41c9_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3ffc4253f4787ba845f2110a772cbb9d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1000' height='1861'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"1861\" data-original-token=\"v2-ed3c6453525a180d741dce8adf396c97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8385dc18e935335feabe320006ae41c9_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3ffc4253f4787ba845f2110a772cbb9d_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ffc4253f4787ba845f2110a772cbb9d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"l5xbvIRu\">也就是说，孩子的大脑先天并没有任何差别，正是因为我们的区别对待，才导致了差别的产生。<br></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"FsW8hKDf\">4</p><p data-pid=\"QDkNx-Pu\">更可怕的是，这样的偏见不但会影响孩子们的能力发展，还会让他们的自信、自我评价甚至人生也都会产生巨大偏差。纪录片中，有这样一个实验：当被问到男孩和女孩有什么不同，23 个 5~11 岁的孩子的答案让所有人震惊了——女孩子们都认为：“男人更擅长领导别人之类的事情。” “我会用漂亮这样的词形容女孩子。”</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9770b93f613de178c9f6824b2f914687_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-c11159ac947c500248f4e2f667dccee3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cc237af8896f71c538737265fa521ec_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-9770b93f613de178c9f6824b2f914687_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-c11159ac947c500248f4e2f667dccee3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cc237af8896f71c538737265fa521ec_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-9770b93f613de178c9f6824b2f914687_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9770b93f613de178c9f6824b2f914687_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4558fa6ed542ab944ff766734ab01ab5_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-61da560b7c65f5570595e1f5d88efcd5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-79d8a06d100657b19577842f03d267f8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4558fa6ed542ab944ff766734ab01ab5_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-61da560b7c65f5570595e1f5d88efcd5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-79d8a06d100657b19577842f03d267f8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4558fa6ed542ab944ff766734ab01ab5_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4558fa6ed542ab944ff766734ab01ab5_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"SBUQHtR6\">”我觉得强壮是专属于男孩子的词汇。”男孩的回答则是：“我觉得男孩比女孩聪明。” “男人更成功，因为他们能担下更多更难胜任的工作。” “男孩子更重要，因为他们更能保护女孩子。”</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3808637e28b0950b20bdac7f7bacf109_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"1688\" data-original-token=\"v2-9bf7e494af5440d747d77b5dffa8000c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c943beb55570d53b5babc7383ea7ce8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3808637e28b0950b20bdac7f7bacf109_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1000' height='1688'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"1688\" data-original-token=\"v2-9bf7e494af5440d747d77b5dffa8000c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c943beb55570d53b5babc7383ea7ce8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3808637e28b0950b20bdac7f7bacf109_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3808637e28b0950b20bdac7f7bacf109_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"6cFsYCav\">甚至还有孩子回答：“男人能简简单单就当上了总统，不是吗？”</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5311c9d6e5ca4feb2878833e65202204_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"705\" data-original-token=\"v2-80c5c32e71cd8babc4e677fcbd3f9567\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7cd05f51c5aa8cc8c2a21e7b8b32a9d3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-5311c9d6e5ca4feb2878833e65202204_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='705'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"705\" data-original-token=\"v2-80c5c32e71cd8babc4e677fcbd3f9567\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7cd05f51c5aa8cc8c2a21e7b8b32a9d3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-5311c9d6e5ca4feb2878833e65202204_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5311c9d6e5ca4feb2878833e65202204_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"DKl_WsEA\">当问到哪些职业是女性会做的？女生的回答是：发型师、保姆和美甲师。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0d9afc89d3874d940ef4bedfb3da882_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"697\" data-original-token=\"v2-a97ac25c17002cd2f326b58d84716946\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b68486cea01208b776be023389d5929d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e0d9afc89d3874d940ef4bedfb3da882_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='697'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"697\" data-original-token=\"v2-a97ac25c17002cd2f326b58d84716946\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b68486cea01208b776be023389d5929d_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e0d9afc89d3874d940ef4bedfb3da882_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0d9afc89d3874d940ef4bedfb3da882_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"co7Bp6yz\">而当问到哪些是男性会做的？男生显然要自信得多：足球运动员、网球运动员、船长。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b295d3ab2951f59df6ea54592128bbbf_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"888\" data-original-token=\"v2-81f6512a4ce769da52c058d56afe4179\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3bd1fb288b6dfca772adc1fc5fd1552_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b295d3ab2951f59df6ea54592128bbbf_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1000' height='888'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"888\" data-original-token=\"v2-81f6512a4ce769da52c058d56afe4179\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3bd1fb288b6dfca772adc1fc5fd1552_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b295d3ab2951f59df6ea54592128bbbf_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b295d3ab2951f59df6ea54592128bbbf_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"MTlrb_A2\">尽管这些孩子最大的才七岁，但他们已经对男女的工作，有了很狭隘的思维定势，而这无形中又形成了限制。测试结果还显示，性别刻板印象让女孩严重低估了自己的聪明程度，自尊与自信程度也都很低。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dffa9332e29d62f4700c17dd97441e9a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-fd388ed169abc335ebc20f1f30bef5c6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b82881ad05b6244d601cbeac3145207_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dffa9332e29d62f4700c17dd97441e9a_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-fd388ed169abc335ebc20f1f30bef5c6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b82881ad05b6244d601cbeac3145207_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dffa9332e29d62f4700c17dd97441e9a_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dffa9332e29d62f4700c17dd97441e9a_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c96107158b2008f1bb1e38406b95a207_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-88578f47516e7b9b233d54179decd018\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6857215f6684ceef4a5a1510ab8da4a1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c96107158b2008f1bb1e38406b95a207_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-88578f47516e7b9b233d54179decd018\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6857215f6684ceef4a5a1510ab8da4a1_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c96107158b2008f1bb1e38406b95a207_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c96107158b2008f1bb1e38406b95a207_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"7ZRmFf2Q\">在测试中，50% 的男孩描述自己是“最棒的”，而只有 10% 的女孩用“最棒的”形容自己。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-bbb0ebe422bf5a0ed5bdf48c777c841b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-eca66d511621d7704e2612f43cff1985\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cd35856b698a8fb4c8cdb03d796b681_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bbb0ebe422bf5a0ed5bdf48c777c841b_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-eca66d511621d7704e2612f43cff1985\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cd35856b698a8fb4c8cdb03d796b681_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bbb0ebe422bf5a0ed5bdf48c777c841b_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-bbb0ebe422bf5a0ed5bdf48c777c841b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac7408062b17d4dc5e4f622d96f81b5b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-ead81cc4c60b2f9b6f5d2c37030e99c0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-146618effc72bc1b37e7e80341f0c4c9_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ac7408062b17d4dc5e4f622d96f81b5b_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-ead81cc4c60b2f9b6f5d2c37030e99c0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-146618effc72bc1b37e7e80341f0c4c9_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ac7408062b17d4dc5e4f622d96f81b5b_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac7408062b17d4dc5e4f622d96f81b5b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"cqVbu8C2\">而男生呢？他们认为坚强是不把情绪表现出来，结果不会表达情绪反而引发了强烈的攻击、冲动、强迫和忤逆行为。</p><p data-pid=\"vvY6Ktju\">5</p><p data-pid=\"dlHdV8q0\">这样的刻板印象，甚至会在成年后也给孩子带来巨大影响和限制。纪录片中，贾维德做了这样一些总结：有数据表明，受<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=180972947&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%84%A6%E8%99%91%E7%97%87&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">焦虑症<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>困扰的女性，更倾向于将问题内化，因此往往会导致孤独，孤僻和抑郁；而总被要求要坚强不能软弱的男孩，则更可能将问题向外表现，由此引发攻击、冲动行为，强迫和忤逆行为。贾维德由此总结了一句话，让人不寒而栗：很多人长大后过上艰难而迷茫的成年生活，究其根本就在于我们如何灌输给他们“做一个男人/女人应该是什么样？”</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a32b17b6b5f74b12d9b3ae78c91a45c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-fd43bbfef224a78595f71fce1b18bf4b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-60b9083c5a051703117d2a3d2ae7c9de_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4a32b17b6b5f74b12d9b3ae78c91a45c_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='608'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-fd43bbfef224a78595f71fce1b18bf4b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-60b9083c5a051703117d2a3d2ae7c9de_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4a32b17b6b5f74b12d9b3ae78c91a45c_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a32b17b6b5f74b12d9b3ae78c91a45c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f42530f48d0bd302db843e52b382edd_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"134\" data-rawheight=\"43\" data-original-token=\"v2-1f42530f48d0bd302db843e52b382edd\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f42530f48d0bd302db843e52b382edd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"134\"/></noscript><div><div class=\"GifPlayer css-o0k2vi\" data-size=\"small\" data-za-detail-view-path-module=\"GifItem\"><img class=\"ztext-gif\" width=\"134\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f42530f48d0bd302db843e52b382edd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f42530f48d0bd302db843e52b382edd_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-size=\"small\" alt=\"动图封面\" style=\"display: block;\"><div class=\"GifPlayer-icon css-d39tw7\"><svg width=\"50\" height=\"50\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><ellipse fill=\"#000\" opacity=\"0.45\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"30\" ry=\"30\"></ellipse><ellipse stroke=\"#FFF\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" opacity=\"0.5\" cx=\"30\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"26\" ry=\"26\"></ellipse></g><svg x=\"16\" y=\"18.5\"><g fill=\"#fff\"><path x=\"100\" y=\"100\" d=\"M12.8422852,12.9814453 L12.8422852,11.3994141 L7.63916016,11.3994141 L7.63916016,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.0517578 L10.9086914,13.3242188 C10.8911133,15.2050781 9.46728516,16.4707031 7.39306641,16.4707031 C5.01123047,16.4707031 3.51708984,14.625 3.51708984,11.6367188 C3.51708984,8.70117188 5.00244141,6.84667969 7.34912109,6.84667969 C9.08056641,6.84667969 10.284668,7.68164062 10.7768555,9.2109375 L12.7543945,9.2109375 C12.3237305,6.64453125 10.2319336,5.00976562 7.34912109,5.00976562 C3.79833984,5.00976562 1.50439453,7.61132812 1.50439453,11.6542969 C1.50439453,15.75 3.77197266,18.3076172 7.36669922,18.3076172 C10.6889648,18.3076172 12.8422852,16.2246094 12.8422852,12.9814453 Z M17.5180664,18 L17.5180664,5.31738281 L15.5493164,5.31738281 L15.5493164,18 L17.5180664,18 Z M22.659668,18 L22.659668,12.7441406 L28.1088867,12.7441406 L28.1088867,11.0039062 L22.659668,11.0039062 L22.659668,7.11035156 L28.6098633,7.11035156 L28.6098633,5.31738281 L20.690918,5.31738281 L20.690918,18 L22.659668,18 Z\"></path></g></svg></svg></div></div></div></figure><p data-pid=\"OC51OxDx\">我们总谈教育，什么是好的教育？有时候，我们做到不定义孩子，不对孩子进行性别预判，淡化男女差异，允许他们有多元化的选择，激发他们的潜能，就足矣。只有当我们大人摆脱性别差异的思维定势，避免给孩子贴上“男孩应该怎样，女孩应该怎样”的标签，才能真正激发孩子内在的潜能，实现多元发展，未来才能拥有更多的可能性。就像纪录片，让人印象深刻的一句话：<b>“如果我们区别对待男孩和女孩，他们就会用同样的方式看待自己，但如果我们平等地对待他们，也许就可以改变他们的看法。”</b></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a1b9b4c01f7d18737fb4fbe420495528_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"887\" data-original-token=\"v2-d3a2cd72392fcc9d55a05ac4e2364019\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1ebc7bfdbe894bb64d4cca244e9e0de7_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a1b9b4c01f7d18737fb4fbe420495528_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1000' height='887'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1000\" data-rawheight=\"887\" data-original-token=\"v2-d3a2cd72392fcc9d55a05ac4e2364019\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-1ebc7bfdbe894bb64d4cca244e9e0de7_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1000\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a1b9b4c01f7d18737fb4fbe420495528_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a1b9b4c01f7d18737fb4fbe420495528_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "1\n\n前段时间，有个小学给孩子们开设了一门特别的“兴趣课”——女生学打毛衣、男生学“做飞机”“造火箭”“装汽车”。学校表示，这么做是为了纠正现在的“男孩、女孩性别错位的现象。”在这所学校的校长看来，“男孩应该豪气蓬勃，女孩该宁静温婉”，但现在的孩子们都在一条轨道上被塑造，都缺乏这种环境。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n这下网友们不乐意了：这是性别专属课还是性别歧视课？谁说女孩只能织毛衣、男孩只能造飞机了？\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n也难怪大家反应这么大：全世界都在努力破除性别偏见，怎么这里反而要开个这样的兴趣班？要知道这样的偏见和观念，无论对男孩还是女孩都没什么好处！\n\n\n\n\n2\n\nBBC有一部纪录片《男女不再有别》，讲",
